         <abstract><p>The <foreign xml:lang="gez">Sǝbḥata fǝqur</foreign> is an office composed of both fixed and optional
            prayers and hymns. It follows the <ref type="work" corresp="LIT1961Mashaf"/> in manuscripts, with whose office that of the
            <foreign xml:lang="gez">Sǝbḥata fǝqur</foreign> is considered to form a unity.</p></abstract>
